# Voice Agent Service

This sub-package implements real-time AI voice agents using the VideoSDK Voice Agent Kit.

## Setup

1. Ensure the virtual environment is active:
   ```bash
   source .venv/bin/activate
   ```
2. Install packages:
   ```bash
   uv pip install -e .
   ```
